OL,5,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FIn North Yorkshire, more than
OL,7,     F1,000 drink drivers are arrested
OL,8,     Fevery year. On one busy road,
OL,9,     Fofficers search for a car
OL,10,     Freportedly swerving on a dual
OL,11,     Fcarriageway, and set a trap.
OL,12,G1400 Traffic Cops
OL,13,     FThis episode covers an alarming
OL,14,     Fsurge in burglary and car theft as
OL,15,     Fpolice units pursue a gang of
OL,16,     Fsuspected car thieves using fake
OL,17,     Fregistration plates to steal
OL,18,     Fhigh-powered vehicles.
